    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat the <strong>pork loin steaks</strong> dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Cover the<strong> steaks</strong> in<strong> cling film</strong> and bash them with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> until evenly flattened to approx. 1cm in thickness</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1676304420585-x200.jpg",
